Productivity

Pomodoro / Focus timer — 25/5 cycles, keyboard space to start/pause when widget is focused.
Quick Notes / Scratchpad — single markdown-rendered textarea, autosaved. Great for "stuff I'll forget."
Habit tracker — small grid of dots for the last 30 days per habit.
Countdown — to a date you set (trip, deadline, birthday).
Calendar month view — read-only, highlights today; optional ICS feed URL.


Information

RSS / Hacker News / Reddit top posts — pick a feed URL, show top 5 headlines.
GitHub activity — your recent notifications or starred-repo releases (needs PAT).
Crypto / Stock ticker — symbols user picks; one row each.
Currency converter — two dropdowns + amount.
Word/quote of the day.

Ambient
Now playing — Spotify/YT-Music via Media Session API or webhook.
Lo-fi / nature sounds — small play button, no autoplay.
Moon phase + sunrise/sunset — pairs nicely with weather (Open-Meteo provides this for free).
World clocks — pick 2–4 timezones.


Personal

Day greeting — "Good morning, Lakshay" with a rotating quote.
Random bookmark / "stumble" — opens a random saved bookmark.
Recently closed tabs (needs sessions permission).
Reading list — articles to read later (URL + title).


Fun / micro

Step-count / wellness (manual or HealthKit-style import).
Dice / random picker — for indecision.
Tiny canvas doodle pad.